=== concepts_of_management_with_microsoft_defender_for_endpoint ===

--- What is Microsoft Defender for Endpoint? ---
> Built to be an enterprise grade endpoint security platform designed to help entyerprise networks prevent, detect, investigate and respond to advanced threats.

--- Microsoft Defender for Endpoint ---
> Endpoint behavioral sensors
> Cloud security analytics
> Threat intelligence
3000 different people world-wide
> Threat and vulnerability management
> Attack surface reduction
> Next generation protection
> Endpoint detection and response
> Automated investigation and remediation
> Microsoft secure score for devices
> Microsoft threat experts

--- Integrations with MS Solutions ---
> Azure Security Center
> Microsoft Sentinel
> Intune
> Microsoft Defender for Cloud Apps
> Microsoft Defender for Identity
> Microsoft Defender for Office 365
